<subSubSection pageId="67" pageNumber="264" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="67.[151,1436,1177,1468]" pageId="67" pageNumber="264">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[196,273,1215,1241]" pageId="67" pageNumber="264">Notes.</emphasis>
The first and so far only record of this rare species from Sardinia is based on the annotation “Sardegna” [= Sardinia] added by hand by Luigioni to his own catalogue (
<bibRefCitation author="Gobbi, G." box="[1096,1248,1253,1279]" pageId="67" pageNumber="264" pagination="29 - 35" refId="ref73450" refString="Gobbi, G. (1973) Aggiunte inedite di Paolo Luigioni al Catalogo &quot; I Coleotteri d'Italia &quot;. Bollettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 105 (1 - 3), 29 - 35." type="journal article" year="1973">Gobbi 1973</bibRefCitation>
). No Sardinian specimens of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Paykull" baseAuthorityYear="1798" box="[312,451,1291,1317]" class="Insecta" family="Histeridae" genus="Saprinus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="67" pageNumber="264" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="virescens">
<emphasis box="[312,327,1291,1316]" italics="true" pageId="67" pageNumber="264">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[342,451,1291,1316]" italics="true" pageId="67" pageNumber="264">virescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
were found in Luigioni’s collection nor in any of the other collections examined by 
<bibRefCitation author="Penati, F. &amp; Vienna, P." box="[151,448,1329,1355]" pageId="67" pageNumber="264" pagination="173 - 175" refId="ref75329" refString="Penati, F. &amp; Vienna, P. (2005) Insecta Coleoptera Histeridae. In: Ruffo, S. &amp; Stoch, F. (Eds), Checklist e distribuzione della fauna italiana. Memorie del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Verona, 2. serie, Sezione Scienze della Vita, 16, pp. 173 - 175, with data on CD-ROM." type="journal article" year="2005">Penati and Vienna (2005</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Penati, F. &amp; Vienna, P." box="[462,537,1329,1355]" pageId="67" pageNumber="264" pagination="173 - 175" refId="ref75399" refString="Penati, F. &amp; Vienna, P. (2006 a) Insecta Coleoptera Histeridae. In: Ruffo, S. &amp; Stoch, F. (Eds), Checklist and distribution of the Italian fauna. Memorie del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Verona, 2. serie, Sezione Scienze della Vita, 17, pp. 173 - 175, with data on CD-ROM." type="journal article" year="2006">2006a</bibRefCitation>
), who nonetheless reported 
<bibRefCitation author="Gobbi, G." box="[869,1051,1329,1355]" pageId="67" pageNumber="264" pagination="29 - 35" refId="ref73450" refString="Gobbi, G. (1973) Aggiunte inedite di Paolo Luigioni al Catalogo &quot; I Coleotteri d'Italia &quot;. Bollettino della Societa Entomologica Italiana, 105 (1 - 3), 29 - 35." type="journal article" year="1973">Gobbi’s (1973)</bibRefCitation>
record. However, given the fact that the additional researches did not provide any new data and that the species is absent also from neighbouring 
<collectingCountry box="[315,404,1404,1430]" name="France" pageId="67" pageNumber="264">Corsica</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Secq, M. &amp; Secq, B." box="[420,643,1404,1430]" pageId="67" pageNumber="264" pagination="65 - 80" refId="ref76247" refString="Secq, M. &amp; Secq, B. (1997) Les Saprinus Erichson de la faune de France (Col. Histeridae), deuxieme partie. L'Entomologiste, 53 (2), 65 - 80." type="journal article" year="1997">Secq &amp; Secq 1997</bibRefCitation>
), I consider the above record to be based on a misidentification and therefore exclude the species from the Sardinian histerid fauna.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
